claim.claim-text:
A data processing apparatus comprising:
a first memory configured to store compensation data;
a data encoding unit configured to classify the compensation data transmitted from the first memory according to frequency components and encode the classified compensation data;
a second memory configured to store encoded data transmitted from the data encoding unit; and
a data decoding unit configured to classify the encoded data transmitted from the second memory according to data components and decompress the classified encoded data.

The data processing apparatus of claim 1, wherein the data encoding unit comprises:
a frequency determining unit configured to classify the compensation data into first compensation data and second compensation data according to frequency components and generate a first flag bit and a second flag bit;
a low frequency encoding unit configured to encode the first compensation data according to the first flag bit and output first encoded data;
a high frequency encoding unit configured to encode the second compensation data according to the second flag bit and output second encoded data; and
an output unit configured to output at least one of the first encoded data and the second encoded data, as the encoded data.

The data processing apparatus of claim 1, wherein the data decoding unit comprises:
a data determining unit configured to classify the encoded data into first encoded data and second encoded data according to flag bit;
a low frequency decoding unit configured to decode the first encoded data and output first decoded data;
a high frequency decoding unit configured to decode the second encoded data and output second decoded data; and
an output unit configured to output at least one of the first decoded data and the second decoded data, as the decoded data.
